Programs License

Programs license management web system.

View project on GitHub
What is the purpose of programs license system ?
  • The system allows companies to manage their programs.
  • Watch our Project Guide on YouTube

More about the System programs license..

  • The library uses the RESTful web services from this website : [http://www.openweathermap.org/]
  • The library has been developed in the java script language, CSS, HTML5, JQUERY.
  • The library has been developed in Aptana environment.
  • Unit testing was performed.
  • The system has been developed as part of the final project in the course 'Web Programming'.

What is included in the library ?

  • A folder with all code.
